snippet.title: Ynglet | Console Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ynglet launches on Playstation and Nintendo Switch!
Playstation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10009065
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/ynglet-switch/

Take a break from all the stresses of the world and unwind to the music of Ynglet while traversing from platform to platform in the strange 2D world. Jump, dash, slide, bounce and float your way through an abstract, effervescent sky. These also include new and more challenging special levels to really test your skills. You think you can travel through the demanding special worlds?
